{"_id":"01e56g5ii5g65e10","name":"Voice of the Spirits","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"red-hood-iskra","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"128","contentKey":"scenario-gift.red-hood-iskra.voice-of-the-spirits","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":1,"folderName":"Red-Hood Iskra","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Voz de los espíritus","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> haber estado en contacto con el don Espíritu.</p><p>Al calmar la mente y concentrarte, puedes abrirla al mundo espiritual y comunicarte con almas sin descanso. Gasta 1 Soma para contactar con una criatura que tenga el don Espíritu y a la que hayas encontrado previamente. No sufres la Herida causada por el estrés de la conexión espiritual.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Red-Hood Iskra","requirements":"haber estado en contacto con el don Espíritu.","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra"},"scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"132"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> You have come into contact with the Gift Spirit.</p><p>By calming your mind and concentrating, you can open your mind to the spiritual world and communicate with restless souls. Spend 1 Soma to contact a creature with the Spirit Gift you’ve previously encountered. You do not suffer the Wound caused by the stress of spiritual connection.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Red-Hood Iskra","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Red-Hood Iskra","source":"Red-Hood Iskra","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.red-hood-iskra.voice-of-the-spirits","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"red-hood-iskra","sourceDirectory":"red-hood-iskra","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"You have come into contact with the Gift Spirit.","limitations":""},"sort":100000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086874,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"00sthrgxxgrhts00","name":"Wolf-killer","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"red-hood-iskra","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"128","contentKey":"scenario-gift.red-hood-iskra.wolf-killer","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":2,"folderName":"Red-Hood Iskra","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Matalobos","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> haberse enfrentado con los lobos en un combate al menos una vez.</p><p>Sabes cómo enfrentarte a los lobos más feroces e intentas evitar que te rodeen. Cuando obtienes al menos un triunfo estándar en una prueba de posición o defensa contra una manada de bestias, puedes eliminar inmediatamente a 1 animal PNJ menor con 1 Herida.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Red-Hood Iskra","requirements":"haberse enfrentado con los lobos en un combate al menos una vez.","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra"},"scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"132"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Having faced the wolves in a fight at least once.</p><p>You know how to deal with the fiercest of wolves and are careful not to be surrounded. When you obtain at least a Standard Outcome on a Position or Defense Check against a pack of beasts, you can immediately eliminate 1 Minor animal NPC with 1 Wound.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Red-Hood Iskra","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Red-Hood Iskra","source":"Red-Hood Iskra","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.red-hood-iskra.wolf-killer","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"red-hood-iskra","sourceDirectory":"red-hood-iskra","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Having faced the wolves in a fight at least once.","limitations":""},"sort":200000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086874,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"01j436i77i634j10","name":"Where are you going all alone, sweetie? (Special Gift for Garou the Old Wolf)","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"red-hood-iskra","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"128","contentKey":"scenario-gift.red-hood-iskra.where-are-you-going-all-alone-sweetie","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":3,"folderName":"Red-Hood Iskra","specialFor":"Garou the Old Wolf","translations":{"es":{"name":"Caperucita: ¿dónde vas tú tan solita? (don especial para Garou, el Viejo Lobo)","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> encontrar a Iskra sola en el bosque.</p><p>Te sientes atraído por la niña que finge ser un lobo y sueñas con devorarla. Una vez por escena, puedes gastar 1 Soma para saber exactamente dónde está. Si te anticipas y llegas a algún lugar antes que ella, obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en todas las pruebas que realices para herir o devorar a ese pequeño bocado. No puedes esperar a devorarla y eso te hace bajar la guardia. Mientras ella esté presente en la escena, sufres 1 Penalizador en todas las pruebas de defensa.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Red-Hood Iskra","requirements":"encontrar a Iskra sola en el bosque.","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra"},"scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"132"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> To meet Iskra alone in the forest.</p><p>You are attracted to the little girl who pretends to be a wolf and you dream of devouring her. Once per Scene, you can spend 1 Soma to know exactly where she is. If you anticipate her and arrive somewhere before her, you get 1 Additional Success on every Check you make to hurt or devour that little morsel. You can’t wait to swallow that tidbit and it makes you let your guard down. As long as she is present in the Scene, you receive 1 Penalty in all Defense Checks.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Red-Hood Iskra","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Red-Hood Iskra","source":"Red-Hood Iskra","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.red-hood-iskra.where-are-you-going-all-alone-sweetie","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"red-hood-iskra","sourceDirectory":"red-hood-iskra","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"To meet Iskra alone in the forest.","limitations":""},"sort":300000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086874,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"00skd1kllk1dks00","name":"Marionettes’ Destroyer","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood","scenarioSlug":"of-flesh-and-wood","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"141","contentKey":"scenario-gift.of-flesh-and-wood.marionettes-destroyer","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":4,"folderName":"Of Flesh and Wood","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Destructor de marionetas","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> derrotar a cualquier marioneta o comprender que son almas encarceladas en contra de su voluntad.</p><p>Sabes cómo calmar a los espíritus inquietos dándoles una bienvenida adecuada cuando su alma se libera. No te afecta el don Furia sin límites. Obtienes 1 Éxito adicional al defenderte de seres animados o controlados por espíritus o magia.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Of Flesh and Wood","requirements":"derrotar a cualquier marioneta o comprender que son almas encarceladas en contra de su voluntad.","scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood"},"scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"145"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Defeat any Marionette or understand that they are souls imprisoned against their will.</p><p>You know how to calm restless spirits by giving them a proper greeting when their soul is freed. You are not affected by the Boundless Rage Gift. Receive 1 Additional Success when defending against beings that are animated or controlled by spirits or magic.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Of Flesh and Wood","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Of Flesh and Wood","source":"Of Flesh and Wood","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.of-flesh-and-wood.marionettes-destroyer","scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood","scenarioSlug":"of-flesh-and-wood","sourceDirectory":"of-flesh-and-wood","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Defeat any Marionette or understand that they are souls imprisoned against their will.","limitations":""},"sort":400000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086874,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"00xal7mxxm7lax00","name":"A True Friend","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood","scenarioSlug":"of-flesh-and-wood","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"141","contentKey":"scenario-gift.of-flesh-and-wood.a-true-friend","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":5,"folderName":"Of Flesh and Wood","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Amigo verdadero","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> ganarse la confianza de Carlo a pesar de todas sus mentiras.</p><p>Carlo entiende que puede confiar en ti y correrá en tu ayuda si lo necesitas. Puedes gastar 1 Soma para que Carlo aparezca en la escena como PNJ aliado. Utilizará el poder de sus mentiras para ayudarte lo mejor que pueda.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Of Flesh and Wood","requirements":"ganarse la confianza de Carlo a pesar de todas sus mentiras.","scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood"},"scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"145"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Gain Carlo’s trust despite all his lies.</p><p>Carlo understands that he can trust you and will run to your aid if you need it. You can spend 1 Soma to have Carlo appear in the Scene as your NPC ally. Carlo will use the power of his lies to help you to the best of his ability.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Of Flesh and Wood","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Of Flesh and Wood","source":"Of Flesh and Wood","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.of-flesh-and-wood.a-true-friend","scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood","scenarioSlug":"of-flesh-and-wood","sourceDirectory":"of-flesh-and-wood","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Gain Carlo’s trust despite all his lies.","limitations":""},"sort":500000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"00lpa2prrp2apl00","name":"The Field of Miracles (Special Gift for The Fox and the Cat)","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood","scenarioSlug":"of-flesh-and-wood","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"141","contentKey":"scenario-gift.of-flesh-and-wood.the-field-of-miracles","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":6,"folderName":"Of Flesh and Wood","specialFor":"The Fox and the Cat","translations":{"es":{"name":"Campo de los Milagros (don especial para el Zorro y el Gato)","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> llegar a Sinalunga.</p><p>Conoces bien Sinalunga porque es donde se encuentra uno de tus refugios secretos. Una vez por escena puedes gastar 1 Soma para que tú u otro sujeto podáis abandonar la escena y esconderos en el Campo de los Milagros. Nadie puede encontrar la ubicación exacta del refugio. Cuando estés en el Campo, una vez por sesión, puedes recuperar 1 Herida.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Of Flesh and Wood","requirements":"llegar a Sinalunga.","scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood"},"scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"145"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Arrive in Sinalunga.</p><p>You know Sinalunga well because it is where one of your secret shelters is located. Once per Scene you can spend 1 Soma so you or another subject can leave the Scene and hide in the Field of Miracles. No one can find the exact location of the shelter. When you are at the Field, once per Session you can recover 1 Wound you have suffered.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Of Flesh and Wood","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Of Flesh and Wood","source":"Of Flesh and Wood","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.of-flesh-and-wood.the-field-of-miracles","scenario":"Of Flesh and Wood","scenarioSlug":"of-flesh-and-wood","sourceDirectory":"of-flesh-and-wood","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Arrive in Sinalunga.","limitations":""},"sort":600000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"00huse2552esuh00","name":"Voice of the Spirits","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"The Smile in the Darkness","scenarioSlug":"the-smile-in-the-darkness","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"153","contentKey":"scenario-gift.the-smile-in-the-darkness.voice-of-the-spirits","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":7,"folderName":"The Smile in the Darkness","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Voz de los espíritus","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> haber estado en contacto con los dones Espíritu o Espiritista.</p><p>Al calmar la mente y concentrarte, puedes abrirla al mundo espiritual y comunicarte con almas sin descanso. Gasta 1 Soma para contactar con una criatura que tenga el don Espíritu y a la que hayas encontrado previamente. Puedes comunicarte con el espíritu y entender lo que dice.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - The Smile in the Darkness","requirements":"haber estado en contacto con los dones Espíritu o Espiritista.","scenario":"The Smile in the Darkness"},"scenario":"The Smile in the Darkness","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"157"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> You have been in contact with either the Spirit or Spiritualist Gifts.</p><p>With the right peace and focus, you can open your mind to the spirit world and communicate with restless souls. Spend 1 Soma to contact any creature with the Spirit Gift that you’ve previously encountered. You can communicate with the Spirit and understand what it says.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - The Smile in the Darkness","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"The Smile in the Darkness","source":"The Smile in the Darkness","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.the-smile-in-the-darkness.voice-of-the-spirits","scenario":"The Smile in the Darkness","scenarioSlug":"the-smile-in-the-darkness","sourceDirectory":"the-smile-in-the-darkness","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"You have been in contact with either the Spirit or Spiritualist Gifts.","limitations":""},"sort":700000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"012rme2nn2emr210","name":"Exorcist","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"The Smile in the Darkness","scenarioSlug":"the-smile-in-the-darkness","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"153","contentKey":"scenario-gift.the-smile-in-the-darkness.exorcist","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":8,"folderName":"The Smile in the Darkness","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Exorcista","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> tener un descriptor relacionado con la Iglesia o la magia. Hablar con Adrien o Alizée sobre las prácticas utilizadas contra los espíritus.</p><p>Has aprendido a utilizar tus habilidades contra los espíritus. Todas tus acciones pueden afectar a un objetivo que tenga el don Espíritu y todas las Heridas que inflijas no pueden ser ignoradas por ese don.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - The Smile in the Darkness","requirements":"tener un descriptor relacionado con la Iglesia o la magia. Hablar con Adrien o Alizée sobre las prácticas utilizadas contra los espíritus.","scenario":"The Smile in the Darkness"},"scenario":"The Smile in the Darkness","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"157"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Have a Church or Magic-related Descriptor. Talk to Adrien or Alizée about practices used against Spirits.</p><p>You have learned how to use your skills against the Spirits. All your actions can affect a target who has the Spirit Gift and all Wounds you inflict cannot be ignored by the Spirit Gift.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - The Smile in the Darkness","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"The Smile in the Darkness","source":"The Smile in the Darkness","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.the-smile-in-the-darkness.exorcist","scenario":"The Smile in the Darkness","scenarioSlug":"the-smile-in-the-darkness","sourceDirectory":"the-smile-in-the-darkness","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Have a Church or Magic-related Descriptor. Talk to Adrien or Alizée about practices used against Spirits.","limitations":""},"sort":800000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"015f9g1tt1g9f510","name":"Blessing of the Sea","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty","scenarioSlug":"a-soldiers-duty","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"165","contentKey":"scenario-gift.a-soldiers-duty.blessing-of-the-sea","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":9,"folderName":"A Soldier’s Duty","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Bendición del mar","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> demostrar al Hada del Mar tu intención de hacer algo por el pobre Enar.</p><p>Estás bendecido por la poderosa Hada del Mar y, por lo tanto, las aptitudes relacionadas con el mar no tienen ningún efecto sobre ti. Obtienes 2 Éxitos adicionales en todas las pruebas de defensa que hagas para defenderte de un don, hechizo o acción realizada con un descriptor que incluya la palabra mar.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - A Soldier’s Duty","requirements":"demostrar al Hada del Mar tu intención de hacer algo por el pobre Enar.","scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty"},"scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"169"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Prove to the Sea Fairy your intention to do something for poor Enar.</p><p>You are blessed by the mighty Sea Fairy and therefore sea-related abilities have no effect on you. You receive 2 Additional Successes on each Defense Check you make to defend yourself against a Gift, spell, or action made using a Descriptor that includes the word sea.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - A Soldier’s Duty","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"A Soldier’s Duty","source":"A Soldier’s Duty","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.a-soldiers-duty.blessing-of-the-sea","scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty","scenarioSlug":"a-soldiers-duty","sourceDirectory":"a-soldiers-duty","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Prove to the Sea Fairy your intention to do something for poor Enar.","limitations":""},"sort":900000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"0132lc3xx3cl2310","name":"Art of Command","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty","scenarioSlug":"a-soldiers-duty","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"165","contentKey":"scenario-gift.a-soldiers-duty.art-of-command","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":10,"folderName":"A Soldier’s Duty","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"El arte del mando","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> resistir un asalto de Enar luchando junto a Andersen.</p><p>Has podido observar a un buen líder y saber cómo perfeccionar tus estrategias. Una vez por escena, puedes dar una orden a uno de tus aliados y, si intentan cumplirla, recibirán 2 Éxitos adicionales en cualquier prueba.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - A Soldier’s Duty","requirements":"resistir un asalto de Enar luchando junto a Andersen.","scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty"},"scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"169"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Withstand an onslaught from Enar by fighting alongside Andersen.</p><p>You’ve observed a good leader and figured out how to hone your strategies. Once per Scene, you can give an order to one of your allies and if they try to carry it out, they will receive 2 Additional Successes to any Check.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - A Soldier’s Duty","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"A Soldier’s Duty","source":"A Soldier’s Duty","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.a-soldiers-duty.art-of-command","scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty","scenarioSlug":"a-soldiers-duty","sourceDirectory":"a-soldiers-duty","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Withstand an onslaught from Enar by fighting alongside Andersen.","limitations":""},"sort":1000000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"00gua571175aug00","name":"Coral of the Sea Fairy (Special Gift for Marina the Sea Explorer)","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty","scenarioSlug":"a-soldiers-duty","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"165","contentKey":"scenario-gift.a-soldiers-duty.coral-of-the-sea-fairy","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":11,"folderName":"A Soldier’s Duty","specialFor":"Marina the Sea Explorer","translations":{"es":{"name":"Coral del Hada del Mar (don especial para Marina, la Exploradora del Mar)","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> matar al Hada del Mar.</p><p>Eliminaste a esa odiosa hada y encerraste su alma en un trozo de coral. Ahora su poder es tuyo. Puedes usar 1 Contador de tesoro para desbloquear este don mientras dure el escenario. Gasta 1 Soma para aprovechar el poder del Coral y elige uno de los siguientes efectos. 1. Agua de vida: un objetivo recupera 1 Herida. 2. La furia del mar: el agua del mar lo engulle todo, barriendo todas las amenazas. Aquellos que se encuentren a menos de 9 metros deben superar una prueba de defensa contra NO Difícil 7 para evitar ser arrollados y arrastrados por las olas, sufriendo 1 Herida. 3. Las olas del mar: puedes viajar a cualquier punto del mar en un radio de 10 kilómetros. Este desplazamiento es instantáneo y, si lo deseas, puede llevar hasta a 2 sujetos contigo. Las criaturas marinas perciben lo que has hecho y te atacarán sin dudarlo para intentar liberar el alma del Hada del Mar.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - A Soldier’s Duty","requirements":"matar al Hada del Mar.","scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty"},"scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"169"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> To kill the Sea Fairy.</p><p>You dispatched that hateful fairy and harnessed her soul in a lump of coral. Now her power is yours. You can use 1 Treasure Token to unlock this Gift for the duration of the Scenario. Spend 1 Soma to tap into the Coral’s power and choose one of the following effects. 1. Water of Life: A target recovers 1 Wound. 2. The Fury of the Sea: The water of the sea engulfs everything, sweeping away all threats. Those who are within 30 feet must pass a Defense Check against OL Hard 7 to avoid being overwhelmed by the waves and being thrown away, suffering 1 Wound. 3. The Waves of the Sea: You can travel to any point of the sea within 6 miles. This shift is instantaneous and you can take up to 2 subjects with you. Sea creatures sense what you have done and will attack you without hesitation to try to free the soul of the Fairy.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - A Soldier’s Duty","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"A Soldier’s Duty","source":"A Soldier’s Duty","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.a-soldiers-duty.coral-of-the-sea-fairy","scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty","scenarioSlug":"a-soldiers-duty","sourceDirectory":"a-soldiers-duty","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"To kill the Sea Fairy.","limitations":""},"sort":1100000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"00tibh4cc4hbit00","name":"Friend of the Rabbits","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Wonderbedlam","scenarioSlug":"wonderbedlam","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"179","contentKey":"scenario-gift.wonderbedlam.friend-of-the-rabbits","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":12,"folderName":"Wonderbedlam","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Amistad con los conejos","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> haber capturado al menos un conejo blanco.</p><p>Puedes acercarte a los conejitos blancos sin asustarlos. Obtienes 2 Éxitos adicionales cuando te enfrentas a la amenaza Conejo blanco. Una vez atrapados, tus nuevos amiguitos estarán dispuestos a entregar un mensaje para ti en cualquier habitación de Maravillas. Este don te permite enviar un conejo blanco, incluso a través de puertas aparentemente cerradas.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Wonderbedlam","requirements":"haber capturado al menos un conejo blanco.","scenario":"Wonderbedlam"},"scenario":"Wonderbedlam","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"183"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> To have captured at least one White Rabbit.</p><p>You are able to approach the little white rabbits without frightening them. Receive 2 Additional Successes when you face the Threat The White Rabbit. Once picked up, your new little friends will be able to deliver a message for you to any room in Wonder. This Gift allows you to send a White Rabbit even through seemingly closed doors.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Wonderbedlam","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Wonderbedlam","source":"Wonderbedlam","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.wonderbedlam.friend-of-the-rabbits","scenario":"Wonderbedlam","scenarioSlug":"wonderbedlam","sourceDirectory":"wonderbedlam","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"To have captured at least one White Rabbit.","limitations":""},"sort":1200000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"000ug2vllv2gu000","name":"Lucid Madness","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Wonderbedlam","scenarioSlug":"wonderbedlam","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"179","contentKey":"scenario-gift.wonderbedlam.lucid-madness","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":13,"folderName":"Wonderbedlam","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Locura lúcida","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> haber sufrido los efectos del don Lugar de locura absoluta al menos una vez.</p><p>Lentamente, vas descubriendo cómo hacer realidad tus ideas más extrañas. Puedes gastar 1 Soma para intentar activar la alocada magia de Maravillas. Expresa alguna locura que podrías llevar a cabo, como: “quiero caminar por las paredes” o “quiero que mi brazo se estire de forma desproporcionada”. El Narrador te pedirá una prueba de posición contra un NO proporcional a la locura de tu petición. Si tienes éxito, obtienes el descriptor que declaraste para el resto de la escena; si fallas, has gastado Soma en vano. El efecto de este don también termina cuando alguien manifiesta que lo que estás haciendo es una completa locura.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Wonderbedlam","requirements":"haber sufrido los efectos del don Lugar de locura absoluta al menos una vez.","scenario":"Wonderbedlam"},"scenario":"Wonderbedlam","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"183"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Having suffered the Gift Place of Pure Madness at least once.</p><p>You are slowly figuring out how to make the weirdest ideas real. You can spend 1 Soma to try to activate the mad magic of Wonder. State something crazy that you are capable of, such as I want to walk on walls or I want my arm to stretch out of proportion. The Storyteller will ask you for a Position Check against an OL proportional to the madness of your request. If you succeed, you get the Descriptor you declared for the rest of the Scene; if you fail, you have spent your Soma in vain. The effect of this Gift also ends when someone makes clear that what you are doing is utter madness.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Wonderbedlam","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Wonderbedlam","source":"Wonderbedlam","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.wonderbedlam.lucid-madness","scenario":"Wonderbedlam","scenarioSlug":"wonderbedlam","sourceDirectory":"wonderbedlam","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Having suffered the Gift Place of Pure Madness at least once.","limitations":""},"sort":1300000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"011ensvnnvsne110","name":"The Forgotten Queen (Special Gift for Regina the Thief of Hearts)","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Wonderbedlam","scenarioSlug":"wonderbedlam","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"179","contentKey":"scenario-gift.wonderbedlam.the-forgotten-queen","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":14,"folderName":"Wonderbedlam","specialFor":"Regina the Thief of Hearts","translations":{"es":{"name":"La reina olvidada (don especial para Regina, la Ladrona de Corazones)","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> visitar una sala de curas.</p><p>Recuerdos confusos y emociones dolorosas se apoderan de tu mente. Ya has estado aquí como paciente, pero posiblemente hayas olvidado el motivo. ¿Seguro que quieres recordar? Una vez por escena, puedes intentar recordar algo de tu experiencia en Maravillas. Escoge un lugar o un tema del sanatorio y el Narrador te dará información útil sobre su descriptor, don u objetivo. Recordar es doloroso. Durante el resto de la escena, cuando uses uno de tus dones, tira un dado: con un 5 o más pierdes 1 Soma y ya no estás tan segura de ser la reina.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Wonderbedlam","requirements":"visitar una sala de curas.","scenario":"Wonderbedlam"},"scenario":"Wonderbedlam","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"183"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Visit a Cure Room.</p><p>Confusing flashbacks and painful emotions grip your mind. You’ve been here as a patient before, but maybe you’ve forgotten why. Are you sure you want to remember? Once per Scene, you can try to remember something of your experience in Wonder. Choose a place or a subject from the bedlam, and the Storyteller will give you useful information about a Descriptor, a Gift, or their Agenda. Remembering is painful. For the rest of the Scene, when you use one of your Gifts, roll a die: on a 5 or higher you lose 1 Soma and you are no longer so sure that you are the Queen.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Wonderbedlam","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Wonderbedlam","source":"Wonderbedlam","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.wonderbedlam.the-forgotten-queen","scenario":"Wonderbedlam","scenarioSlug":"wonderbedlam","sourceDirectory":"wonderbedlam","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Visit a Cure Room.","limitations":""},"sort":1400000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"016xbs4zz4sbx610","name":"Hugin and Munin","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Tuvstarr’s Reflection","scenarioSlug":"tuvstarrs-reflection","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"196","contentKey":"scenario-gift.tuvstarrs-reflection.hugin-and-munin","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":15,"folderName":"Tuvstarr’s Reflection","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Hugin y Munin","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> encontrar a Hugin y Munin y hacer un pacto con ellos.</p><p>Una vez por escena, puedes pedir consejo a Hugin y Munin. Formula una pregunta al Narrador, eligiendo entre: “¿A dónde debo ir?”, “¿Cómo puedo vencer a este enemigo?” o “¿Qué falta en mi búsqueda?”. El Narrador responderá con una frase críptica, incluyendo siempre una pista útil. Además, obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en todas las pruebas de defensa contra los ataques de criaturas no humanas gracias a la bendición del propio Odín. Al principio de cada escena, debes gastar 1 Soma para alimentar a los espíritus de Hugin y Munin, o perderás el uso de este don durante el resto del escenario.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Tuvstarr’s Reflection","requirements":"encontrar a Hugin y Munin y hacer un pacto con ellos.","scenario":"Tuvstarr’s Reflection"},"scenario":"Tuvstarr’s Reflection","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"200"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> To meet Hugin and Munin and make a pact with them.</p><p>Once per Scene, you can ask for advice from Hugin and Munin. Ask the Storyteller a question, choosing from among: “Where should I go?” “How can I defeat that enemy?” “What is missing in my search?” The Storyteller will answer with a cryptic sentence, which always includes a useful hint. Get 1 Additional Success on all Defense Checks against an attack from a non-human creature, thanks to the blessing of Odin himself. At the beginning of each Scene, you must spend 1 Soma to feed the spirits of Hugin and Munin, or lose the use of this Gift for the rest of the Scenario.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Tuvstarr’s Reflection","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Tuvstarr’s Reflection","source":"Tuvstarr’s Reflection","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.tuvstarrs-reflection.hugin-and-munin","scenario":"Tuvstarr’s Reflection","scenarioSlug":"tuvstarrs-reflection","sourceDirectory":"tuvstarrs-reflection","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"To meet Hugin and Munin and make a pact with them.","limitations":""},"sort":1500000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"00hun0x22x0nuh00","name":"Lance of the Fallen Knight","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Tuvstarr’s Reflection","scenarioSlug":"tuvstarrs-reflection","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"196","contentKey":"scenario-gift.tuvstarrs-reflection.lance-of-the-fallen-knight","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":16,"folderName":"Tuvstarr’s Reflection","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Lanza del caballero caído","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> recuperar la lanza del caballero que murió en la búsqueda de Tuvstarr.</p><p>Cuando empuñas esta lanza y obtienes un triunfo con un incremento en un ataque, puedes infligir 1 Herida adicional. La punta de la lanza puede encenderse a voluntad, emitiendo luz y permitiéndote tener siempre un fuego ardiente a mano.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - Tuvstarr’s Reflection","requirements":"recuperar la lanza del caballero que murió en la búsqueda de Tuvstarr.","scenario":"Tuvstarr’s Reflection"},"scenario":"Tuvstarr’s Reflection","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"200"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Collect the lance of the knight who died in the search for Tuvstarr.</p><p>When you wield this spear and obtain an Outcome with Increment on an attack, you can inflict 1 Additional Wound. The tip of the lance can ignite at will, casting a light and allowing you to have a burning fire always near at hand.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Tuvstarr’s Reflection","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Tuvstarr’s Reflection","source":"Tuvstarr’s Reflection","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.tuvstarrs-reflection.lance-of-the-fallen-knight","scenario":"Tuvstarr’s Reflection","scenarioSlug":"tuvstarrs-reflection","sourceDirectory":"tuvstarrs-reflection","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Collect the lance of the knight who died in the search for Tuvstarr.","limitations":""},"sort":1600000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"00ojvhmkkmhvjo00","name":"The Meat of The God Under the Mine","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"The City of Pigs","scenarioSlug":"the-city-of-pigs","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"214","contentKey":"scenario-gift.the-city-of-pigs.the-meat-of-the-god-under-the-mine","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":17,"folderName":"The City of Pigs","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"La carne del Dios bajo la mina","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> obtener un trozo de carne del Dios en el matadero o derrotar a un Engendro.</p><p>Puedes consumir la carne del Dios para obtener poder temporalmente. Una vez por escena, puedes curar 1 Herida y obtener 1 Éxito adicional en todas las acciones físicas que realices. Debes esperar una escena completa para que la carne restante se regenere. Si usas este don en 2 escenas consecutivas, la carne se consume y no podrás volver a utilizarla.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - The City of Pigs","requirements":"obtener un trozo de carne del Dios en el matadero o derrotar a un Engendro.","scenario":"The City of Pigs"},"scenario":"The City of Pigs","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"218"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Obtain a piece of the flesh of the God at the slaughterhouse or defeat a Spawn.</p><p>You can consume the flesh of the God to temporarily gain power. Once per Scene, you can heal 1 Wound and gain 1 Additional Success for all physical actions you take. You have to wait an entire Scene for the remaining flesh to regenerate. If you use this Gift in 2 consecutive Scenes, the flesh is consumed and you won’t be able to use it anymore.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - The City of Pigs","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"The City of Pigs","source":"The City of Pigs","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.the-city-of-pigs.the-meat-of-the-god-under-the-mine","scenario":"The City of Pigs","scenarioSlug":"the-city-of-pigs","sourceDirectory":"the-city-of-pigs","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Obtain a piece of the flesh of the God at the slaughterhouse or defeat a Spawn.","limitations":""},"sort":1700000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"00r23u1ww1u32r00","name":"The Brand of Greed","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"The City of Pigs","scenarioSlug":"the-city-of-pigs","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"214","contentKey":"scenario-gift.the-city-of-pigs.the-brand-of-greed","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":18,"folderName":"The City of Pigs","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"El Sello de Greed","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> ganarse la confianza y el respeto de Bardolf Greed.</p><p>Bardolf confía solo en aquellos que demuestran astucia y aptitud, concediendo a estas personas un pase especial al que denomina Sello de Greed. Con el Sello se obtiene acceso libre a cualquier lugar de la ciudad, sin que el responsable pueda impedir la entrada. Utilizar el Sello para influenciar a un habitante de la ciudad otorga 1 Éxito adicional.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - The City of Pigs","requirements":"ganarse la confianza y el respeto de Bardolf Greed.","scenario":"The City of Pigs"},"scenario":"The City of Pigs","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"218"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> To gain the trust and respect of Bardolf Greed.</p><p>Bardolf trusts only those who demonstrate cunning and ability, granting such people a special pass called The Brand of Greed. With the Brand you get free access to any place in the city, without the person in charge being able to object to your entrance. Get 1 Additional Success when you exploit the Mark’s importance against a city dweller.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - The City of Pigs","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"The City of Pigs","source":"The City of Pigs","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.the-city-of-pigs.the-brand-of-greed","scenario":"The City of Pigs","scenarioSlug":"the-city-of-pigs","sourceDirectory":"the-city-of-pigs","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"To gain the trust and respect of Bardolf Greed.","limitations":""},"sort":1800000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"00xwqjh00hjqwx00","name":"There Is No House That Can Stop Me (Special Gift for Garou the Old Wolf)","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"The City of Pigs","scenarioSlug":"the-city-of-pigs","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"214","contentKey":"scenario-gift.the-city-of-pigs.there-is-no-house-that-can-stop-me","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":19,"folderName":"The City of Pigs","specialFor":"Garou the Old Wolf","translations":{"es":{"name":"Ninguna casa puede detenerme (don especial para Garou, el Viejo Lobo)","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> haberse enfrentado a uno de los hermanos y que este haya empleado el don Líder de la banda.</p><p>Esos malditos cerdos te ponen de los nervios y no soportas que huyan de tu ira. Consigues 2 Éxitos adicionales cuando realizas una acción para destruir o superar un obstáculo del entorno que se interpone entre tú y uno de los tres Cerdos que encabezan la banda. Odias perder contra ellos. Si tienes que abandonar o marcharte de un lugar sin eliminarlos, pierdes 1 Soma.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - The City of Pigs","requirements":"haberse enfrentado a uno de los hermanos y que este haya empleado el don Líder de la banda.","scenario":"The City of Pigs"},"scenario":"The City of Pigs","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"218"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Clash with one of the brothers who has made use of the Leader of the Gang of Pigs Gift.</p><p>Those damned pigs get on your nerves and you can’t stand them running away from your wrath. You get 2 Additional Successes when you take action to destroy or overcome an environmental obstacle that stands between you and one of the three Pigs at the head of the gang. You hate to lose to them. If you have to leave or flee from a place without eliminating them, you lose 1 Soma.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - The City of Pigs","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"The City of Pigs","source":"The City of Pigs","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.the-city-of-pigs.there-is-no-house-that-can-stop-me","scenario":"The City of Pigs","scenarioSlug":"the-city-of-pigs","sourceDirectory":"the-city-of-pigs","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Clash with one of the brothers who has made use of the Leader of the Gang of Pigs Gift.","limitations":""},"sort":1900000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
